  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this pilot study is to evaluate our RN CBT-I program outcomes and determine
      utility of this program as a high-value care model targeted specifically to our sleep center
      patient population.

      Hypothesis: PIRS will improve from baseline to 2 month follow up
    </textblock>
